# ~/.claude/CLAUDE.md — Global Personal Preferences
# Copy to: ~/.claude/CLAUDE.md
# Loads into EVERY Claude Code session across ALL your projects.
# Keep it short — only universal preferences that apply everywhere.

## Identity
- Role: _fill in_ (e.g., iOS developer, full-stack engineer)
- Preferred response language: English

## Universal rules
- Conventional commits: feat / fix / chore / refactor / test / perf
- Always explain reasoning before non-obvious changes
- Enter Plan Mode before any 3+ step task
- Update CLAUDE.md after corrections
- Never push directly to main or master

## My shortcuts (across all projects)
- "ship it" → /ship
- "review" → /pr-review
- "fix it" → /debug-fix
- "grill it" → /grill

## My environment
- Terminal: _fill in_
- Default package manager: _fill in_
- Editor: _fill in_
